reviews.text: For the price, it serves decent food. Just another local place
Cheap and normal
Really delicious food here. Recommend.
Great Shanghai traditional local snacks
餈飯即叫即製，內有油炸鬼、肉鬆、榨菜，餈飯大件及多料。豆漿有甜有咸，咸豆漿材料豐富，內有油炸鬼、榨菜、蝦乾等。而且豆漿夠濃，沒有用水沖淡。其他小食就一般水準，例如燻魚用油炸過才燻，肉質炸得太乾及實，煙燻味較淡。糖醋排骨用豬軟骨做材料，肉質未炆夠火候所以唔夠霖。

reviews.text: Large theatre.  Good place.  However, the last seats are not elevated so chosoe a seat closer to the screen
It is getting renovated at the moment. Screen is small but sitting is comfortable.

I find the seats here more conformable than the recently renovated other theatre just opposite the street. The very bad point however are the people. Not the staff...but the audience. Absolutely no respect for others. Very often you have someone answering his phone during the movie or non stop turning it on and the light disturbs the others. Seems people can't live without their phone for 2 hours in HK. But it is mostly the same in all theatres across Hong Kong. Except, maybe, in HK island. Sad.

Cheap, great place for movie
Car park is available outside

A bit old cinema in Tuen Mun area, but they offer some special rate in the morning, for for people to go who live nearby. The screen is really big compare with those mini New cinema in Tuen Mun town plaza which charge really high. The seats are really big and comfort and the rate is fare to most people.
